name: Mr Bao at Home
description: Dumplings delivered to your door, to cook at home. Delivery catchment area is 2 miles and costs £3 per drop-off. Pork, chicken, and veggie available to steam straight from frozen. 20 for £15, 40 for £25. To order your little bit of Mr Bao at home, email with your type, amount, address, and phone number.
